This web application serves as a complete cafeteria menu and recipe guide for students and staff. Users can select a meal type—Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner, or Snacks—and view a list of items available under that category. By clicking on any item, the app displays the full recipe, including all ingredients and step-by-step instructions to prepare the dish. This interactive platform not only helps users decide what to eat but also provides practical cooking guidance, making it a fun and useful tool for anyone looking to explore easy and delicious meals.
